  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"zephr-anchor\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNovacrystals\u003c/strong\u003e are an equipment material in \u003cem\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/monster-hunter-wilds/40940\"\u003eMonster Hunter Wilds\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e. You’ll have a chance at collecting them from \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/monster-hunter-wilds-guide/528887/ore-locations-list-minerals-shard-crystal-mining-outcrop\"\u003emining outcrops\u003c/a\u003e once you reach \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/monster-hunter-wilds-guide/528902/high-rank-how-to-unlock-hr-soft-caps\"\u003eHigh Rank\u003c/a\u003e or earn them as rewards for certain High Rank hunts.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou’ll need novacrystals to forge weapons like the Final Battleaxes and armor like the Gypceros Coil.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur \u003cem\u003eMonster Hunter Wilds \u003c/em\u003eguide will tell you \u003cstrong\u003ewhere to find novacrystals\u003c/strong\u003e and how to collect them.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"where-to-find-monster-fluid-in-monster-hunter-wilds\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eWhere to find novacrystals in Monster Hunter Wilds\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-novacrystal-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1622\" data-pswp-width=\"2880\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Monster Hunter Wilds using the map filter to find mining outcrops\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-novacrystal-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C1