r come High Rank hunts like:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHunting an HR Rey Dau in \u003cstrong\u003e“When the Dust Settles …”\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHunting an HR Nu Udra in \u003cstrong\u003e“Sinister Sneer”\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHunting an Arkveld in \u003cstrong\u003e“The Chains of Life”\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHunting an HR Ajarakan and a gravios in \u003cstrong\u003e“Troublemakers”\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHunting an HR Xu Uu and Guardian Ebony Odogaron in \u003cstrong\u003e“The Struggle to Surive”\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"how-to-collect-extra-mining-outcrop-resources\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHow to collect extra mining outcrop resources\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1622\" data-pswp-width=\"2880\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-dragonbone-relic-1.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn \u003cem\u003eMonster Hunter Wilds\u003c/em\u003e armors, talismans, and decorations all give you skills. At level 3, the \u003cstrong\u003eGeologist skill\u003c/strong\u003e gets you one extra item from mining outcrops per time you interact with them.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eEquipment like the \u003cstrong\u003eGeology Charm \u003c/strong\u003etalisman, \u003cstrong\u003eChainmail \u003c/strong\u003earmor, and \u003cstrong\u003eGeology Jewel\u003c/strong\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/monster-hunter-wilds-guide/533238/decorations-how-to-get-equip-grind\"\u003edecorations\u003c/a\u003e all give you the Geologist skill. For mining outcrops, you only get a benefit at the third level of the skill, so you’ll need three pieces that give you the skill — like the Chainmail Headgear, Armor, and Gloves.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Geologist skill also doesn’t add to the number of times you can collect something from a mining outcrop — you still only collect three times per visit. It does, however, increase the number of items you pull out with each time you hit Circle/B.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo also help you understand \u003cem\u003eMonster Hunter Wilds\u003c/em\u003e, we explain \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/monster-hunter-wilds-guide/529576/capture-monsters-endemic-life-how-to\"\u003ehow to capture monsters\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/monster-hunter-wilds-guide/519994/change-weapons-swap-switch-secondary\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ehow to change weapons\u003c/a\u003e, provide some \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/e/528147\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eSeikret tips\u003c/a\u003e, and teach you how \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/e/526390\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003elayered armor\u003c/a\u003e works.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
